<plot>While 4,400 aircraft mechanics wage a seemingly endless strike, one of them, Roy Koch, and his daughter, follow Roy's outsourced job to China. 'The Red Tail' follows this unlikely duo of "working-class nobodies" as they discover the intricate paths that have lead us here, and the real power of solidarity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?586039</url></doc>
